  data:
    redis:
      host: localhost   # or your k8s service
      port: 6379
```

👉 If running in Kubernetes:

```yaml
spring:
  data:
    redis:
      host: redis.ns-<your-namespace>.svc.cluster.local
      port: 6379
```

